trans-unit.source: Enumerates types of speech synthesis events.
trans-unit.target: Räknar upp typer av tal sammanfattande händelser.

trans-unit.source: Custom speech synthesis engines define the types of events submitted to the Speech platform synthesizer infrastructure with the TtsEventId.
trans-unit.target: Anpassade tal sammanfattande motorer definiera vilka typer av händelser som skickats till tal synthesizer plattformsinfrastrukturen med TtsEventId.

trans-unit.source: Specification is performed by setting the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo.EventId%2A> property of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> instances passed to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.AddEvents%2A> member of the class implementing the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> interface passed to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A> method on a custom speech engine's implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>.
trans-unit.target: Specifikationen utförs genom att ange <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo.EventId%2A>egenskapen för <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>instanser skickades till <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.AddEvents%2A>medlem i den klass som implementerar <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite>gränssnittet överförs till <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A>metoden på en anpassad tal-motor implementering av <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>.</xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml> </xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A> </xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> </xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.AddEvents%2A> </xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> </xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo.EventId%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Speech platform infrastructure indicates the type of events it is currently handling through the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> property on the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> passed to the speak implementation.
trans-unit.target: Plattformsinfrastrukturen tal som anger vilken typ av händelser som för närvarande hanterar via den <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>egenskapen på den <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite>skickades till speak implementeringen.</xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> </xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>

trans-unit.source: The value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> is a bitmask, where the members of TtsEventId define the location of the bit corresponding to the event type.
trans-unit.target: Värdet för <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>är en bitmask där medlemmarna i TtsEventId definiera platsen för den motsvarande biten för händelsetypen.</xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, WordBoundary has a value of five (5), meaning the fifth bit in the value returned by <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> indicates if the site supports the event type.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel WordBoundary har värdet fem (5), vilket innebär att den femte biten i värdet som returneras av <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>Anger om platsen har stöd för händelsetypen.</xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>
